00:00:04.110 --> 00:00:08.090
We all know that NOAA satellites help

00:00:08.110 --> 00:00:12.100
us forecast weather on Earth. But did you know that some weather satellites

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:16.140
also forecast weather in space? 

